{"tid":829120,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝搭地鐵撞鳩個唔識排隊嘅廢老 感覺好爽","createTime":"2018-09-20T07:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T05:47:33.000Z","uid":75440,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"27dc05dfb0a2defe020b4974a8dcc56e86203e4e","tid":829120,"uid":75440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"今朝番工搭MTR<br />\n大家好好地排隊排兩邊<br />\n有個廢老無啦啦排中開果行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果下我發緊呆仲未有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n車門開果下<br />\n因為好多人落車佢搵唔到位ZIP上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到乘客落哂車<br />\n排中間嘅廢老第一時間衝上車<br />\n然後我係廢老後面加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從後撞到佢差D跌低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到廢老回過神嘅時候<br />\n可能太多人上車<br />\n佢四圍望都搵唔番岩岩係邊個撞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後淨係妹下妹下咁口up up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb16e1fa5e7e53c1f515465556b2b5fdcf752db4","tid":829120,"uid":210314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fdbae01339e9d7a4f0030be269b2b22ff242d2","tid":829120,"uid":164839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c6b2b69a28f5faf8b4da9ce5a742ca78a402ae","tid":829120,"uid":86614,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"比較陰濕左d<br />\n人地擺明居馬光明正大打占<br />\n你暗箭傷人"},{"pid":"d773f58104067332f8b7a3aa952415ec478d8a83","tid":829120,"uid":75440,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86c6b2b69a28f5faf8b4da9ce5a742ca78a402ae","tid":829120,"uid":86614,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":1